## File Layout Rules
- Screens: `src/features/[feature]/[name]-screen.tsx`
- Routes: `src/app/` ‚Äî file name becomes the URL path (Expo Router)
- API calls: `src/lib/api/driver/` ‚Äî one file per resource type
- Types: `src/lib/types.ts` ‚Äî keep in sync with adtruck-proof-main
- Always use `@/` absolute imports ‚Äî never `../` relative imports
- Never edit `android/` or `ios/` directories directly ‚Äî use Expo config plugins

